				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BA%A1-Tr%C4%83n/Bi%C3%AAn-c%E1%BA%A3nh/poem-glbctpgZsDML36OtywLITw">Biên cảnh - 邊警</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BA%A1-Tr%C4%83n/author-1SPKfkHlUAnw6r-glqobvQ">Tạ Trăn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/B%C3%ACnh-Nam-ti%C3%AAn-sinh-v%C3%A3ng-B%E1%BA%AFc-k%E1%BB%B3-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng-ch%C6%B0-th%C3%A2n-h%E1%BB%AFu-du-T%E1%BB%AD-Tr%E1%BA%A7m-s%C6%A1n-t%E1%BB%B1-%C4%91%E1%BB%99ng-giai-t%C3%A1c-tr%E1%BB%8Bch-th%E1%BB%8B-b%E1%BB%99-v%E1%BA%ADn-d%C4%A9/poem-QQHzwmKsI8ODPnjCxZROxQ">Bình Nam tiên sinh vãng Bắc kỳ đồng chư thân hữu du Tử Trầm sơn tự động giai tác trịch thị bộ vận dĩ đáp - 屏南先生往北圻同諸親友遊紫沉山寺洞佳作擲示步韻以答</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Bao/%C4%90%E1%BB%99-H%C3%A0-B%E1%BA%AFc/poem-wsMYqiwOLz04pt1HWLY7jQ">Độ Hà Bắc - 渡河北</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Bao/author-r_gVqunh13UrLWcU_1Uqsg">Vương Bao</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82u-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tu/H%E1%BA%A1-Lao-t%C3%A2n/poem-FTxz6F0mr0sghSobdBOCWw">Hạ Lao tân - 下牢津</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82u-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tu/author-Rh6zapU4AwLAuhG1Xl_FMw">Âu Dương Tu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/H%C3%A0nh-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-nh%C3%A0n-thu%E1%BA%ADt/poem-9qDBpgmtaVftFem4LyYgLg">Hành Dương nhàn thuật - 衡陽閒述</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%B4i-L%E1%BB%97/Hoa-Thanh-cung-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-TAzn83iq3p-OP1Sz3SlliQ">Hoa Thanh cung kỳ 2 - 華清宮其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%B4i-L%E1%BB%97/author-D0kSTyyLojSiroomgDKkWw">Thôi Lỗ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-T%C3%B4ng-Quai/L%E1%BA%A1ng-th%C3%A0nh-h%C3%ACnh-th%E1%BA%AFng/poem-iC7Odvt86tzAn7ewHKrJWQ">Lạng thành hình thắng - 諒城形勝</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-T%C3%B4ng-Quai/author-O3detUF1vCJmYx4NhKKivw">Nguyễn Tông Quai</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/Ph%C3%B9-dung-n%E1%BB%AF-nhi-lu%E1%BB%B5/poem-R9STBdCyvV6_VYrjugG5yQ">Phù dung nữ nhi luỵ - 芙蓉女兒誄</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/Th%C3%B4n-d%E1%BA%A1/poem-RWLbMwVDbWoVSbL2EDG8yA">Thôn dạ - 村夜</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%BAc/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-thi%C3%AAn-h%C3%A1-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-nh%E1%BA%A5t-h%C3%B9ng-quan-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-onOP-GxE33SDyhsVfYnnng">Thướng thiên há đệ nhất hùng quan kỳ 1 - 上天下第一雄關其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%BAc/author-DYGad0thHvgCxK3Szp1zVQ">Trần Đình Túc</a>)<br></div>	</div>
